@startuml
title Web client — journey with ETA, persistence, and dashboard refresh (reference sequence)

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam maxMessageSize 240

actor "User" as U
participant "DemoPage\n(Vue)" as Vue
participant "FastAPI\n(main.py)" as API
participant "SUMOSimulation" as Sim
participant "Inference\n(ETA model)" as Inf
database "PostgreSQL\n(journeys)" as PG

== Page load (simulation already up) ==
Vue -> API : GET /api/network/data
API -> Sim : get_network_data()
Sim --> API : edges, junctions
API --> Vue : draw map

Vue -> API : GET /api/simulation/status
API -> Sim : status / time
API --> Vue : is_running, trips, …\n+ polling in UI

== Pick trip ==
U -> Vue : click start edge,\n then destination edge

Vue -> API : POST /api/simulation/calculate-route-by-edges
API -> Sim : calculate_route_by_edges()
Sim --> API : route edges, distance, duration
API --> Vue : highlight path

== Start journey (ETA + run) ==
U -> Vue : Start / Play (main control)
Vue -> API : POST /api/simulation/start-journey
API -> Sim : add_journey_vehicle(\n  start_edge, end_edge, route_edges)
Sim -> Inf : run ETA on graph snapshot
Inf --> Sim : predicted ETA (seconds)
Sim --> API : vehicle_id, start times,\n distance, **predicted_eta**
API --> Vue : show start time, ETA,\n begin playback

== End of trip (metrics) ==
Vue -> API : POST /api/simulation/complete-journey
API -> Sim : finalize duration / error
Sim --> API : actual duration, abs error, accuracy
API --> Vue : update on-screen result

== Persist + refresh analytics ==
Vue -> API : POST /api/journeys/save
API -> PG : insert Journey row
PG --> API : journey_number
API --> Vue : success

Vue -> API : GET /api/journeys/recent, statistics,\nplot endpoints (as implemented)
API -> PG : query aggregates
PG --> API : rows / metrics
API --> Vue : refresh **Recent journeys**,\n performance panels

@enduml
